{"tid":27779,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"四議員覆核案法院下周四作指示","createTime":"2016-12-07T14:02:50.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-07T14:27:45.000Z","uid":47558,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"8f0bbe3853cc0a5cb5137e4f92636825a647eb9f","tid":27779,"uid":47558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-07T14:02:50.000Z","msg":"【Now新聞台】律政司入稟司法覆核四名議員劉小麗、姚松炎、梁國雄和羅冠聰的案件，高等法院下周四開庭作出指示。<br />\n<br />\n法官區慶祥向涉案相關人士發出傳訊令，包括早前以私人身分入稟覆核的莫嘉傑。<br />\n<br />\n傳訊令指出法庭會就入稟人身分，是否合適及在司法覆核有結果前，暫緩執行褫奪四人職務等作出指示。同時，亦會就案件聆訊排期。<br />\n<br />\n律政司要在星期一前，向法院提交入稟理據。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=203008\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D203008&d=miRruejfEI4R7cScey8rnIscwJTI%2BQouKF8MUrnyvY0%3D&h=3378341c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D203008&h=18a6707a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=203008</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n準備 rip 得 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"00994b8624acf2f82795f4ae7bbb265fe314194a","tid":27779,"uid":30044,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-07T14:06:18.000Z","msg":"事實如此<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ac6041fd96670b8c7a06029d0469a8d9460b9a44","tid":27779,"uid":47558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-07T14:11:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>事實如此<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n泰博單野會否出事 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2332fbc8a96f775af5b11b89c09427c2ef07895c","tid":27779,"uid":30044,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-07T14:27:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>事實如此<img src=\"/assets